#define ANIMESH_STRENGTH 2500
#define STAND "Squat"
#define LAND "Crouch"
#define WALK "Cheerful"

#define GREETINGS  ["You stand here in our presence, %s? You are barely a shadow of a true warrior.", "Men are such fragile creatures; perhaps you should find a gentler pursuit, %s.", "I see no strength in you, %s. Go, before you embarrass yourself.", "You have the ambition of a child and the physique of a weakling, %s.", "Your mere presence is an insult to the discipline of my sisters, %s.", "You sweat, you strain—yet you achieve so little, %s.", "A marginal improvement, perhaps, but still a man's clumsy effort, %s.", "Do you truly believe this effort compares to the grace of an Amazon, %s?", "You labor in vain, %s. You lack the blood of the gods.", "It is almost pathetic to watch you struggle with such trivial weights, %s.", "You are stronger than most men, %s—which is to say, you are barely noticeable.", "I see you trying, %s. Keep laboring, it gives you something to do.", "You have found some semblance of utility, %s. Do not let it go to your head.", "Your strength is a flicker, %s. The women of Themyscira burn like the sun.", "You are tolerable for one of your kind, %s.", "You demonstrate surprising discipline, %s. Perhaps there is hope for you yet.", "A competent effort, %s. Rare for a man to show such resolve.", "You are approaching the threshold of being useful, %s.", "Your form is adequate, %s. Even men can learn if they are taught correctly.", "I have seen lesser warriors, %s. You are rising in my estimation.", "You fight with a spirit that almost honors our standards, %s.", "Finally, a man whose strength is worth measuring, %s.", "I respect your focus, %s. A trait rarely seen in the male kind.", "You carry yourself with honor, %s. I will watch your development.", "You are nearing true potential, %s. Do not falter now.", "You possess a magnitude of power that is unexpected, %s.", "You stand tall, %s. It is refreshing to see a man with actual might.", "Your evolution is significant, %s. You hold my respect.", "You are a warrior, %s. You are nearly equal to the standards we set.", "I have been refined by battle, yet you hold your own, %s.", "You are a titan among men, %s. Truly, you possess a god-like power.", "Your strength resonates with the foundations of the earth, %s. Incredible.", "I have reached the peak, and you stand beside me, %s. It is an honor.", "You have achieved a level of perfection that even my sisters would envy, %s.", "At last, an equal. Your power is absolute, %s."]

#define WrestleWin ["Your steel is brittle, and your spirit is untested. Leave this place, %s.","It brings me no joy to lay you low, but the sanctity of this place must be maintained.","You are unversed in the art of war, %s. Seek counsel before you strike again.","I have not even needed to unsheathe my blade. Begone, %s.","You offer no challenge to the daughters of Themyscira. Do not return.","A spirited attempt, %s, but you lack the training of a true warrior.","You fight as if you are dancing, %s. A battle requires far more discipline.","Do you truly seek glory in such a display, %s? You have much to learn.","The ground has claimed you, %s. Learn from this defeat.","I have bested many foes; you are but another whose blade has failed.","You possess courage, %s. That is the first step toward true strength.","A decent skirmish, %s. You hold your ground better than most.","You are not without merit, %s, but you have yet to master your own power.","I enjoyed the challenge of your steel, %s. It was… acceptable.","You fall today, %s. But keep your eyes on the horizon; you have potential.","You fight with conviction, %s. That is the mark of a worthy adversary.","Well struck, %s! It has been some time since a stranger forced me to parry.","You understand the weight of a shield, %s. That is rare among your kind.","A battle of true intent! You have my respect, %s.","The contest is over, %s. Stand tall; you fought with honor.","Your prowess is undeniable, %s! You are a warrior of great renown.","I am invigorated by this clash! You possess the fury of the storm, %s.","You have pushed me to my limits. I am honored to call you my opponent, %s.","Few can mirror my strikes as you have, %s. You are a formidable champion.","A battle of great consequence! You hold the strength of a true hero, %s.","At last, a warrior who knows the true path of the blade! A glorious victory, %s!","The Fates themselves watched our battle, %s. You are a titan among mortals.","You possess the spirit of an Amazon! It was an honor to win against such might.","I have seen few who can withstand my onslaught, %s. You are a champion indeed.","You are a master of arms, %s. To be bested by you would be an honor, but today, the victory is mine!","By the gods, you are magnificent, %s! A clash for the legends of our history!","You possess a power that reaches toward the heavens! An honor to survive this duel, %s.","You are the finest warrior I have faced in an age, %s. You have earned my eternal respect.","Your strength is absolute! Let this victory be sung throughout the ages, %s!","You are the paragon of combat, %s. The world is fortunate to have you."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["How unexpected... a momentary lapse in my focus. You are fortunate, %s.","The Fates have woven a strange tapestry today. I concede this, %s.","You strike with a hidden strength. I will not be caught unaware again.","I am humbled. Your victory is a mystery I shall contemplate.","You have proven stronger than your appearance suggests, %s.","You are a formidable foe, %s. I have underestimated your reach.","You fight with an unconventional style that caught me off guard, %s.","I yield the ground, but keep your honor, %s.","You are a warrior of hidden depths, %s. A hard-fought lesson for me.","I must return to the training grounds. You have opened my eyes, %s.","A noble victory, %s. You possess the heart of a true champion.","You have surpassed my expectations, %s. Your path is one of great strength.","The order of the battle has changed, and you are the victor, %s.","I accept this outcome. You have bested me in combat, %s.","Well fought, %s. You have earned your place in this arena.","You have achieved what few ever have, %s. Your spirit is immense.","I am bested. You carry a strength that is both refined and dangerous, %s.","You fight with a clarity I did not anticipate. You have won this day, %s.","I yield. You are a warrior of undeniable prowess, %s.","A victory of magnitude! You have commanded the battlefield, %s.","Your resolve is equal to the greatest legends, %s. I concede with honor.","I feel the weight of your power. It is profound, %s.","You have outmatched a warrior of Themyscira! I am truly stunned, %s.","A victory of incredible spirit. You are the architect of your own fate, %s.","You are a beacon of strength. I have been bested by a great soul, %s.","We are truly peers in strength. This victory is yours, %s.","You have challenged the heavens and prevailed! A feat of unimaginable spirit, %s.","I have met my match. You are a power that must be acknowledged, %s.","A struggle of mythic proportions. You are triumphant, %s!","You have mastered the battlefield today. I have been overcome, %s.","You are the convergence of all things strong. You have conquered, %s.","Truly, you are an apex of existence. I stand in awe of your triumph, %s.","You have rewritten the prophecy. You are the warrior the world awaits, %s.","A victory that shall reverberate through eternity. I bow to your might, %s.","You are the new standard. It was an honor to fall to such a singular being, %s."]
